title: NFL Week 10 Picks Against the Spread + Bryant McFadden on Steelers-Panthers (Football 11/09)
description:
Ryan Wilson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down the Panthers-Steelers game and tell tales of yore about the 2008 Steelers. Then Will Brinson and R.J. White make picks against the spread for every single game on the Week 10 slate.
